api gateway - single entrypoint for client to interact with multiple microservice ,one time implementation of security

simplify client experience

manage complexities of backend (authentication,security)



1.create starter prj > apigateway

2.add dependency gateway and in pom.xml remove "-mvc",eureka discovery client

3.api configuration properties{id,uri,predicates}

lb->load balancing in uri

server.port=9090

