angular to connect with other service we us @Crossorigin(*) annotation in backend

debugging in front end -> ctrl+shift+i ->network(when making server call)->check name details preview/response/payload(sending data)

by default angular expect reponse as string so whenever we are returning we need to give {reponsetype:'text'} in http client call



